          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h4>Don't crash diet</h4>
            <p>Severe calorie restriction triggers metabolic adaptation, lowering BMR by up to 20%. Keep deficits moderate (500-750 cal below TDEE) for sustainable results.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h4>Prioritize sleep</h4>
